<div style="margin-top:8px;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:${MUTED};">
  🟡 Weekly round winner &nbsp;|&nbsp; 🟢 Prize winner &nbsp;|&nbsp; 🔴 Bonus tip (9/9)
